  "rationale": "Copy-first evidence page in brief order. Hero adapts hero-case-lead: a left copy column with an Angel City FC case card counterweight carrying the 300%+ pulled stat and read action. Story renders three atomic feature-items in a clean trio. Results is a compact stat-block panel with two real metrics as an array. Testimonial reuses the tab-stats split shape with a verbatim attributed quote. Pricing is the intentionally-absent use case, so a Relume pricing-repeated-grid fallback carries three atomic card records \u2014 no table. Closing reuses the deep-teal conversion band with filled + outlined actions. Fixed the closing actions sizeClass from the invalid 'control' to 'body'; all headings stay sentence-case serif display, accent orange confined to marks/controls, no dark bands mid-run."
